never ever never use the downloads that are zipped then when opened say that you have to go to a site to get a password to unlock the files. It exposes you to credit card fraud, identity theft, and identifies you as a pirate torrent user for legal prosecution of intellectual properties theft. Real torrent providers do not require you to fill out surveys, if they do it  is a bogus link and do not download!
